  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE A NEW PENALTY FOR ANY PERSON WHO KILLS ANOTHER PERSON WHILE DRIVING UNDER THE INFLUENCE; TO REQUIRE A PERSON CONVICTED OF DRIVING UNDER THE INFLUENCE TO PAY CHILD SUPPORT TO THE CHILD OF ANY PERSON KILLED AS A RESULT OF THE VIOLATION; TO BRING FORWARD SECTION 63-11-30, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, WHICH PROVIDES THE PENALTIES FOR DRIVING UNDER THE INFLUENCE, FOR PURPOSES OF AMENDMENT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
